ates\",\"completed\":true},{\"text\":\"Re-run the required Gradle test with the pinned GraalVM to verify the fix\",\"completed\":true}]}}\n{\"type\":\"turn.completed\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3583642,\"cached_input_tokens\":3491072,\"output_tokens\":19243,\"reasoning_output_tokens\":9861}}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
